item.title: By: Curt Stone
item.dc:creator: Curt Stone
item.description: <p>Brilliant. Glad all went well in Boston. Going there myself on Wednesday to an accepted student day at MassArt. This is my oldest son's first choice for college this fall. Looking forward to it. Best of luck with your new xPages adventure.</p>
